        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Don't you want to tell me what a little girl like you did in a big city, and-and read me part of that Paris letter I saw the postman give Jane this afternoon?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
