        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "The command is to sleep as little as possible to keep the nerves in a good condition-\"eight hours at the most, and seven would be better.\" What earthly good would a seven hour nap do me?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
