        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "To see me stagger out of my perfectly nice bed at six o'clock every morning now would wring the sternest heart with compassion and admiration at my faithfulness-to whom?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
