        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"Jane,\" I said, looking past her head, \"my health is not very good, and you can bring my breakfast to me in bed after this.\" Poor mr Carter always wanted breakfast on the stroke of seven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
