        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "It was the dearest old-fashioned tune ever written, and Billy sang the words as distinctly as if he had been a boy chorister doing a difficult recitative.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
