        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Lift me up, and I can put him in the waterglass on your table.\" He held up one muddy hand to me, and promptly I lifted him up into my arms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
