        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "He don't know no good songs like 'Black eyed Susan' or 'Little Boy Blue.' I go to sleep quick 'cause he makes me feel tired with his slow tune what's only good for frogs and things.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
