    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "He never stopped coming to see me occasionally, and mr Carter liked him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I'm not sore, why should you be?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Aren't you happy with me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I was just planning a gorgeous dinner party I want to have for her when you came so suddenly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Do you think we could arrange it for Tuesday evening?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"Good gracious, Molly, don't knock the town down like that!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"Help!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Let my kinship protect me!\" exclaimed Tom in alarm, and he pretended to move an inch away from me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000036_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000036_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Then we both laughed and began to plan what Tom called a conflagration.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Miss Clinton was delightfully gracious about the dinner-I almost called it the debut dinner-and the expression on the judge's face when he accepted!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I was glad she was sitting beside him and couldn't see. Some women like to make other women unhappy, but I think it is best for you to keep them blissfully unconscious until you get what you want. Anyhow, I like that girl all over, and I can't see that her neck is so absolutely impossibly flowery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "That, mrs Johnson just couldn't stand, and she came across the street immediately and called me back to the gate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"He's just a week younger, mrs Johnson, and I wouldn't tie him for worlds, even if I married him,\" I said meekly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Well, I must go home now to see that Sally cooks up a few of mr Johnson's crotchets for supper.\" And she began to hurry away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000044_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000044_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "She doesn't know it yet; but I do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I'll never forget my first real party.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000046_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000046_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I can hardly stand thinking about how he looked even now.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000046_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000046_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Candle light, pretty women's frocks, black coat sleeves, cut glass and flowers are good ingredients for a joy drink, and why not?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I sat down at the long table by the window and slowly prepared to enjoy myself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000048_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000048_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I had just lifted it high in the air when out of the lilac scented dark of the garden came a laugh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "The spoon crashed on the table, and I turned and crashed into words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"You are cruel, cruel, john Moore, and I hate you worse than I ever did before, if that is possible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I'm hungry, hungry to death, and now you've spoiled it all!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000051_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000051_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "I was glad myself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Again I had that sensation of being against something warm and great and good, and I don't know how I controlled it enough not to-to-",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"Thank you, I will, all of it, and the bread and butter, too,\" he answered, in that detestable friendly tone of voice, as he drew himself up and sat in the window.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"Supper,\" I sniffed, as I spread the jam on those lovely, lovely slices of bread and thick butter that I had fixed for my own self.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "\"I am so tired of that apple toast combination now that I forget it if I can.\" As I handed him the first slice of drippy lusciousness, I turned my head away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4111_184448_000056_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4111/184448/4111_184448_000056_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4111",
        "content": "Forget-\" He didn't finish his sentence, and I'm glad.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
